      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=ofi4a5jiwz]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ofi4a5jiwz]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=yc7vl7dx62]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=yc7vl7dx62]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=hvgedbzqj1]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hvgedbzqj1]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=zdfndly0mn]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=zdfndly0mn]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=n2rc7al9w3]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=n2rc7al9w3]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ako67it7u9]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ako67it7u9]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=hphk11lzhd]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hphk11lzhd]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=lno5rv5393]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=lno5rv5393]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=yj6cunlzgi]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=yj6cunlzgi]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"french-bakery-banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758105667747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604569601/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758105667747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"541\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604143669\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"french-bakery-banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"fb64f84b-32b8-4aad-b866-99363b9edde2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758105667747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758105667747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"hphk11lzhd\">Project</span></strong>:  Creating a French Bakery</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"n2rc7al9w3\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Marion Machelard, Emma Siret, and C&eacute;line Soubrane</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ako67it7u9\">Edited by:</span></strong> Leif Pedersen</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/Tutorials/French_Bakery/French_Bakery.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758105581313&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604569601/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758105581313&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604569678\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"cbb9a88c-d5b5-4272-ac6b-6e6172a4c81a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758105581313&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758105581313&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>It's 7 am. Dawn covers the shop windows and pastry in golden light. The smell of warm bread fills the room. The first croissants come out of the oven... Nothing better to start a good day than the French way, of course! Enter this immersive scene where rustic charm and traditional French craftsmanship come to life.</p><p>First, let us introduce you to this project. This set is part of a short film, named L&egrave;che-Vitrine, imagined by Marion Machelard, following our studies. The idea was to make a short film with friends while working on our respective jobs. </p><p>As group work is an integral part of our jobs, it's always very stimulating to carry out this type of project together, which is why we'd like to present this tutorial this way. Starting with C&eacute;line Soubrane on modelling, Emma Siret on texturing/shading, and Marion Machelard on lighting/compositing. </p><p>Hope you will find this instructive!</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657424415/Bakery+Modeling\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657424415\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"barkery_modelling_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/barkery_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589849984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604569601/barkery_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589849984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391670\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"barkery_modelling_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"9ab23570-d8ef-4d38-b470-39d91bf72d95\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/barkery_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589849984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/barkery_modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589849984&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"CreatingaFrenchBakery-Modeling\"><span data-colorid=\"lno5rv5393\">Modeling</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/656998602/Bakery+Texturing\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656998602\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"barkery_texturing_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/barkery_texturing_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589928676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604569601/barkery_texturing_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589928676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656834640\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"barkery_texturing_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"353fb8c9-c2d3-45be-af86-7ca89f9825a4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/barkery_texturing_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762589928676&amp;ca