t-alias=\"barkery_comp_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"cec7b95a-c8e2-4f6a-bb05-18f151fb2fa3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/barkery_comp_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590187791&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/barkery_comp_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590187791&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"CreatingaFrenchBakery-Compositing\"><span data-colorid=\"yc7vl7dx62\">Compositing</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h3 id=\"CreatingaFrenchBakery-AbouttheArtist\">About the Artist</h3></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/c%C3%A9line-soubrane-83a747240/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"seline-soubrane-headshot.png\" width=\"201\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/seline-soubrane-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106692417&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=201\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604569601/seline-soubrane-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106692417&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"603979843\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"seline-soubrane-headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"cf882a39-757e-440e-a0f0-58a46b16cc63\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/seline-soubrane-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106692417&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=402&amp;height=402 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/seline-soubrane-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106692417&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=201 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong>C&eacute;line Soubrane</strong></p><p>After studying animation and VFX, C&eacute;line Soubrane is a CG artist specializing in environments. She currently works at Quantic Dream as an environment artist on Star Wars Eclipse.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/emma-siret-6697a5237/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"emma-siret-headshot.png\" width=\"201\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/emma-siret-headshot.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758106708224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=201\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604569601/emma-siret-headshot.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758106708224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604012608\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"emma-siret-headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"19a8a6e1-535f-4427-a56a-ec7c6681a737\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/emma-siret-headshot.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758106708224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=402&amp;height=402 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/emma-siret-headshot.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758106708224&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=201 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong>Emma Siret</strong></p><p>Graduated from ESMA, Emma Siret is a freelance CG artist specializing in modeling and texturing. Passionate about visual creation, she&rsquo;s always looking for new opportunities!</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/marion-machelard-83770124a\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"marion-machelard-headshot.png\" width=\"201\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/marion-machelard-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106715205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=201\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604569601/marion-machelard-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106715205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"603947077\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"marion-machelard-headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604569601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"0b5c9ff3-12ae-432f-8844-f2fad9eab3b4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/marion-machelard-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106715205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=402&amp;height=402 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604569601/marion-machelard-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758106715205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=201 1x\" /></span></a><p>Marion Machelard</p><p>Graduated from ESMA in 2023, Marion joined Red Parrot Studios on a feature film as a lighting artist. Passionate about atmospheres and colors, she's passionate about the possibilities in storytelling.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"b6454db3-4b7d-434d-93d6-9e390e2f42d7\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div 